My quickshell setup in development.
It has been replaced by Noctalia in my daily setup, but will still be developed.  

===== Folder structure =====
Source file is shell.qml where all wanted modules are enabled.
./modules/ holds all top-level modules like the menu bar.
./common/ holds global variables and components used several times, especially colors
All components of top-level modules are in their own directory in the project's root directory, e.g. ./modules/MenuBar.qml imports everything unique from ./menubar/
